### 🟣 PILLAR 5: SRE — `src/sre/` (Phases 22–25)

**Goal:** The model is live. Now protect it, scale it, explain it, and keep it green.

**Serving Stack:**
```
serve.py             (FastAPI server: GET / → samos_dashboard.html, POST /predict)
    ↑ Imported and run by uvicorn
```

**Traffic & Reliability:**
```
mab_gateway.py       (Thompson Sampling MAB: stable vs. candidate traffic split)
cascading.py         (Model cascade: route easy queries to tiny model, hard to large)
autoscaler.py        (CPU/RAM-based HPA simulation)
failover.py          (High-availability failover logic)
rollback.py          (Automated version rollback on accuracy drop)
```

**Monitoring & Safety:**
```
thermal_watchdog.py  (nvidia-smi polling → cooling pause at 85°C) ← IMPORTED BY TRAINING
concept_drift.py     (PSI-based distribution shift detection)
proactive_drift.py   (Forecasts drift before it becomes critical)
incident_response.py (Autonomous SRE bot: detects → mitigates → post-mortems)
alert_formatter.py   (Formats telemetry alerts for webhook delivery)
notif.py             (Webhook notifications to Slack/PagerDuty)
opentelemetry_trace.py (OpenTelemetry distributed tracing)
jaeger_tracer.py     (Jaeger span export)
```

**Operations & Explainability:**
```
power_optimizer.py   (Green-AI: CPU/RAM governor, Carbon-intensity scheduling)
resource_auction.py  (Economic resource allocation via auction theory)
planetary_latency.py (Multi-region CDN latency simulation)
llm_explainer.py     (LLM-generated natural language prediction narratives)
threshold_tuner.py   (Strategic P/R threshold optimization)
meta_optimizer.py    (Pipeline efficiency audit)
ct_loop.py           (Continuous training trigger on drift detection)
```

**Self-Documentation:**
```
live_docs.py         (Auto-generates markdown docs from module docstrings)
wiki_gen.py          (Generates GitHub Wiki content)
walkthrough_gen.py   (Generates video script walkthroughs)
diagram_generator.py (Generates Mermaid/ASCII architecture diagrams)
visualizer.py        (Terminal dashboard visualizer)
meta_critic.py       (Phase 25: Audits every previous phase output for completeness)
sunset_manager.py    (Model lifecycle: deprecates old versions after N days)
multi_lang_cards.py  (Generates model cards in multiple languages)
nlp_orchestrator.py  (NLP-based pipeline control in plain English)
nlp_deploy.py        (Human-aligned deployment via natural language instructions)
stress_test_v2.py    (Locust-based inference load testing)
chaos_monkey_v2.py   (Terminates random services to test resilience)
chaos_mesh.py        (Chaos Mesh Kubernetes chaos injection)
