## Part 4: The Complete Data Flow (End-to-End)

```mermaid
graph TD
    A["Raw Data / APIs / Files"] --> B["Phase 1: ingest.py → Bronze Lake"]
    B --> C["Phase 2: validate.py + semantic_guard.py"]
    C --> D["Phase 3: mask_pii + privacy + sovereignty"]
    D --> E["Phase 4-5: process.py → features.csv"]
    E --> F["Phase 6-8: genealogy + active_learning + RLHF"]
    F --> G["Phase 9-10: train.py + automl.py + nas.py"]
    G --> H["Phase 11: knowledge_graph.py"]
    H --> I["Phase 12-13: evaluate.py + bias_audit.py"]
    I --> J["Phase 14: adversarial.py + chaos testing"]
    J --> K["Phase 15-16: watermark + compliance + ledger"]
    K --> L["Phase 17-21: serve + harden + red-team + optimize"]
    L --> M["Phase 22-25: autoscale + MAB + drift + incident response"]
    M --> N["serve.py: FastAPI Production Server"]
    N -->|"Drift Detected"| G
```

